---

## 3. How to Reproduce the Results

1. Install the dependencies listed in `requirements.txt`.  
2. Run the main notebook `CV_Final_Project_Manasa_Maram-Final.ipynb` (or the script in `code/`).  
3. The outputs will be written automatically into the `results/` folder with the filenames listed above.

These sample images are intended for use in the written report and the project video to visually demonstrate each stage of the Simple World vision pipeline.
